      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation with solid everyday usefulness. It shows its age and would best suit a value-focused buyer, commuter, or hands-on owner looking for practical motoring at a highly accessible price. A straightforward option with real potential for someone who appreciates honest value.",
