      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runabout with a lot of potential for the right buyer. Great as a budget commuter, first car, or weekend project. If you\u2019re after something affordable and don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC, this could be a really solid buy. Priced to sell and ready for someone to make the most of it.",
