      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with plenty of life left. Starts up, runs, and moves out well, with a strong motor feel, solid gearbox response, and the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it a great budget commuter, project base, or utility car. Cosmetics show age and use, but the core package is straightforward and usable. If you want affordable transportation with real value and a platform that still feels capable on the road, this one is worth a look.",
